item.title: Some Interesting Bits
item.description: I whispered in his ear “I love you” he said delighted: “repeat it in my other ear so I regain my balance…” If I had more time I would written a shorter letter. – Cicero I always feel that a man and a woman who do not like the same films will eventually divorce. – Jean-luc Godard
